<Page x:Class="AsynAwaitExamples.Steps.Step22_ParallelForEachAsync"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:vm="clr-namespace:AsynAwaitExamples.ViewModels"
      Title="Step 22 - Parallel.ForEachAsync">
    <Page.DataContext>
        <vm:Step22ViewModel/>
    </Page.DataContext>
    <ScrollViewer VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto">
        <StackPanel Margin="10">
            <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HeaderStyle}" 
                       Text="Step 22: Parallel.ForEachAsync"/>

            <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource ExplanationStyle}" xml:space="preserve">PARALLEL.FOREACHASYNC: The modern async-friendly parallel loop (.NET 6+).

Processes a collection in parallel with built-in concurrency control.
Unlike Task.WhenAll (all at once) or SemaphoreSlim (manual throttling),
Parallel.ForEachAsync has a clean API with MaxDegreeOfParallelism built in.

Unlike the old Parallel.ForEach (synchronous, blocks threads), this version
is fully async. It uses await internally and returns a Task you can await.

WHEN TO USE:
- Processing many items with async I/O (downloading files, API calls).
- You want controlled parallelism without manual SemaphoreSlim wiring.
- You need cancellation support.</TextBlock>

            <Button Style="{StaticResource ActionButton}"
                    Content="?? Basic: process 10 items (max 3 concurrent)"
                    Command="{Binding BasicDemoCommand}"
                    IsEnabled="{Binding IsRunning, Converter={StaticResource InvertBoolConverter}}"/>
            <Button Style="{StaticResource ActionButton}"
                    Content="?? Compare: sequential vs parallel"
                    Command="{Binding CompareDemoCommand}"
                    IsEnabled="{Binding IsRunning, Converter={StaticResource InvertBoolConverter}}"/>
            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                <Button Style="{StaticResource ActionButton}"
                        Content="?? With cancellation (20 items)"
                        Command="{Binding WithCancellationCommand}"
                        IsEnabled="{Binding IsRunning, Converter={StaticResource InvertBoolConverter}}"/>
                <Button Style="{StaticResource ActionButton}" Margin="10,5,0,5"
                        Content="Cancel" Background="#E63946"
                        Command="{Binding WithCancellationCancelCommand}"
                        IsEnabled="{Binding IsRunning}"/>
            </StackPanel>

            <TextBox Style="{StaticResource OutputStyle}" Height="280"
                     Text="{Binding OutputText, Mode=OneWay}"/>
        </StackPanel>
    </ScrollViewer>
</Page>
